SEAWEED CHIPS with NUTShealthy low carb snacking that is satisfyingThere is so much goodness packed into this portable snack Seaweed offers the broadest range of minerals of any food on the planetcontaining 10 20 times the mineral concentration of land plantsplus it s high in protein and fiberThat s why a serving can be only 25 100 calories and packed with flavor and nutrients It s an excellent source of iodinevitamin A K and a very good source of folatemagnesiumironand calcium Seaweed also contains measurable amounts of vitamins C and Ewhich help the absorption of all the other good stuff It satisfies a salty craving and helps many people reap the benefits of sea vegetables who otherwise would notI usually munch on RAW NUTS because roasting them may alter and damage the polyunsaturated fats that nuts contain which is vulnerable to oxidationRoasted nuts are yum so don t eliminate themtotallythe heart healthy monounsaturated fats remain intact as this fat can tolerate higher temperaturesI store my nuts in the fridge or freezer for freshness to prevent rancidityRancid oils are pro inflammatory and carcinogenicThe more the surface of the nut is exposed to airthe more likely it will be to oxidiseRoastedchoppedand ground nuts go rancid more quickly than whole raw oneslowcarbsnackseaweedchipsnutsalmondswholefoodsrealfoodnutritionsatisfyingpaleovegan weightlossfoodfitfoodfitfoodiejroguljfoodinstafoodpicinstafoodporninstahealthysnacksinstahealthybodyinstafitfaminstabloggerinstainspireinstagraminstadailynutritionist
